    • Laptop

      public Laptop(double weight, double width, double height, double depth, double batteryCapacity, double displayInches, double cpu, int systemMemory, int memoryRom, String operationalSystem)
      Constructor with parameters. Decimal params cannot be negative. String params cannot be null.
      Parameters:
      weight - Weight of an appliance, preferably in kilos.
      width - Width of an appliance, preferably in cm.
      height - Height of an appliance, preferably in cm.
      depth - Depth of an appliance, preferably in cm.
      batteryCapacity - Battery capacity of an appliance, preferably in hours.
      displayInches - Display diagonal of a laptop in inches. Cannot be greater than hypotenuse of width and height.
      cpu - CPU power of a laptop. In GHz.
      systemMemory - System memory capacity of a laptop. In Megabytes.
      memoryRom - ROM capacity of a laptop. In Megabytes.
      operationalSystem - OS of a laptop.
